data.description: The Seller is MOTIVATED and offering a $5,000 credit towards closing costs. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath property nestled in the sought-after community of Logan's Reserve offers the perfect blend of modern comfort, picturesque surroundings, and convenience.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the spacious  9' ceilings and bamboo hardwood floors. The first room to the left is perfect for an office or play area. To the right is a half bath. Next is the freshly painted living room and kitchen with  ample space that is perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones.  Complete with 2023 dark grey appliances, granite countertops, extra tall cabinetry, and a massive island for all your quick meals, cooking, and food prep needs. To the right is a mudroom connected to the garage and to the left,  adjacent to the kitchen is the dining area, providing the ideal setting for enjoying family meals or hosting dinner parties.       Upstairs there's plenty of room for a growing family. To the left is a full bath for the three generously-sized bedrooms that offer versatility for a kids room, home office, playroom, or guest quarters, ensuring everyone has their own space. The large laundry room is conveniently located in the hall way between the bedrooms, so no lugging laundry up and down the stairs! At the the end of the hall sits the primary bedroom, with a big walk in closet to the right and to the left a full bath with a dual sink vanity.       Below is the unfinished basement, a perfect area to create your own unique space.       Logan's Reserve community offers an array of amenities for residents, including a clubhouse, swimming pool, basketball court, putting green, walking/jogging trails and a sense of community that you'll love coming home to. Experience the joy of living in a neighborhood that embraces an active and fulfilling lifestyle. Conveniently located just minutes away from I-83, makes it an easy commute south to Maryland, or North to Harrisburg. This homes location is also a short drive to many public parks! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and serenity that this home in Logan's Reserve has to offer!
